description: This data was generated in June 2018. It is a reference list of Data Type labels and IDs. More details: These IDs are used in the table TARGET_metadata_sample_data_availability to map samples to Data Types.

fields.description: A unique ID, representing the combination of the data type (isb_label) and genomic build. These IDs are used in the table TARGET_metadata_sample_data_availability to map samples to Data Types.
fields.name: metadata_data_type_availability_id

fields.description: An ISB defined Data Type, which is used in the ISB-CGC Web App to allow users to filter data by Data Type; e.g. Somatic_Mutation, Protein_Quantification, Pathology_Image, etc.
fields.name: isb_label
